"categories: <a href=\"/catalog/hoodie/\">hoodies</a>, <a href=\"/catalog/"
"tshirts/\">t-shirts</a> and <a href=\"/catalog/long-sleeve/\">longsleeves</"
"a>. Every model is designed in Ukraine, printed on our own DTF equipment, "
"and made from fabrics chosen to withstand daily wear, laundering and any "
"climate — from summer heat to damp autumn."

msgid ""
